Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.41,0:00:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.61,0:00:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.08,0:00:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.62,0:00:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.73,0:00:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.94,0:00:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.74,0:00:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.02,0:01:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.13,0:01:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.47,0:01:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.00,0:01:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開地球的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.57,0:01:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙殖民衛星的生活裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.77,0:01:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋找新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.94,0:01:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.31,0:01:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉正義及和平為名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以壓倒性的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.15,0:02:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓制著各個殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.79,0:02:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在後殖民紀元AC195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.96,0:02:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰名稱[流星作戰]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.80,0:02:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和聯合反目的部份衛星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.23,0:02:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定把偽裝為流星的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.11,0:02:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這次作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早已被聯合總部發覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.33,0:02:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一話\N[少女看見的流星]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在洛蘭捷點AF1至G2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現有物體移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.64,0:03:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距離到達地球\N大氣層還有六百秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只一個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，雷達上有五個金屬反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.85,0:03:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之預先通知大氣層的部門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.82,0:03:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正是以前\N人造衛星的碎片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.09,0:03:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.79,0:03:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉\N報告說有隕石落下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,監視衛星的人還真是沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.17,0:03:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隕石會採用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.73,0:03:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衝入大氣層的上部軌道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.27,0:03:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然如OZ總部的情報所講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.31,0:03:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是殖民衛星的M作戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這艘運輸船能捕捉多少個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.08,0:03:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能捕捉墜落\N尤拉西亞東部那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一個也夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.89,0:03:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在前線的軍人不應急於立功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.99,0:03:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的話好認真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.43,0:03:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過吧，我是個軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,角度沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,7分鍾後開始作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民航穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.79,0:04:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德利安大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.49,0:04:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本穿梭機現在要衝入大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全起見，請你扣好安全帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要離開座位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做甚麼?莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去地球妳那麼不滿嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，非常不滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.84,0:04:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，工作關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.31,0:04:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能好好陪妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，下次去宇宙時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你抽多點時間陪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.21,0:04:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標相對速度01545
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.46,0:04:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自動LOCK ON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊落下降障礙物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的攻擊運輸機!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捕捉到了，映在螢幕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是想誕生新戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人稱[戰爭之卵]的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,M作戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.65,0:05:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民航穿梭機在面前他只有減速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.55,0:05:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會有可能擊落穿梭機加速嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不能做那種張揚的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.92,0:05:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為對方也要秘密行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被聯合纏上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要擊落它嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們衝入大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.84,0:05:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於來到了，這就是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛船改變了航道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想自殺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被燒成灰燼也就能保守秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是那樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是!飛船繼續加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.99,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道他想逃走?不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.79,0:06:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他無理由能抵受那麼高溫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.83,0:06:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，也不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.83,0:06:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的敵人\N看來擁有很高的科技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.20,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是衝入大氣層用的飛船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流星作戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉，這是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人的新武器原來是戰鬥機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.64,0:06:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直和雀鳥一樣的戰鬥機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.17,0:06:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到達飛行高度，能夠攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好試用機槍威嚇祂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，對方不會給威嚇到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊落祂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.58,0:07:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然他們的目的是運送新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.95,0:07:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但駕駛飛船的是操縱它的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠安然脫身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務改變?追擊我的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是OZ的機動戰士運輸機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.24,0:07:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從速度看來載有三部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務改變，知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即擊落OZ運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.08,0:07:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人戰鬥機掉頭向我們飛來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.09,0:07:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能用[里歐]嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.59,0:07:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...你想用機動戰士對付那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但高速機動戰士[艾亞利玆]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比陸戰用的里歐適合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的里歐已經夠快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.60,0:07:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我不能對\N挑戰我的人太冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.81,0:07:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.81,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾亞利玆準備好就會去支援你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?上面嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左面推進系統有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好精彩，傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就完了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.57,0:08:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.50,0:08:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收回里歐\N還是叫艾亞利玆去追?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,返回運輸機，在地面捉祂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.47,0:08:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要調查M作戰的意圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是不可多得的獵物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會自爆嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得來到地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.61,0:08:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒人會想不踏上地面就死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成機動戰士!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.66,0:08:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉那是甚麼設備!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合和OZ之外，想不到還有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有製造機動戰士的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特尉，之後請交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那強度，難道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管，消滅祂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一部!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.25,0:09:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是一擊兩部艾亞利玆就...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉，你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事，要你擔心對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.98,0:10:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經用我的方法弄妥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.22,0:10:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥時的資料分析已經完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從敵人機動戰士的強度看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極可能是由鋼彈合金製成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.63,0:10:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那果然是鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算機身沒有受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.60,0:10:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看那個不要命的駕駛員\N也難逃一死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.60,0:10:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特尉，海軍的航空母艦要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.60,0:10:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將搜索海中未經登錄機器人的工作交給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法，你就轉告他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.60,0:11:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們要尋找的東西就沉沒在\N亞洲區域的JAP座標點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.10,0:11:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.10,0:11:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要把搜索工作交給他們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.10,0:11:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在這一種只急於立功的軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未來不太光明呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德利安先生，請問在這一次的\N殖民地高峰會議中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們做了哪些討論呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問殖民地自治體\N對聯合政府的要求是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請您發表一些談話吧\N德利安先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問殖民地\N何時會發動攻擊呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在地球一直在談論那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.76,0:11:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請發表一下，德利安先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早已恭候大駕，德利安先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍隊的車已在外面等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請立即上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.78,0:11:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在立即嗎，那就頭痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.35,0:12:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在一定要\N準備慶祝小女生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.08,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也已經準備了車送小姐回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，不用擔心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.02,0:12:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我一個人也懂得回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我們去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賽普提姆將軍正在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.08,0:12:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，我的生日很快就到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.08,0:12:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是普通小孩我已經在慶祝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍用機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.75,0:12:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.92,0:12:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡應該能更快成為宇宙港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.56,0:12:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.63,0:12:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥服!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是軍人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要叫人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.88,0:13:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說被擊落了三部機動戰士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.62,0:13:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這種男人會失手真是出乎意料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.63,0:13:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要花點工夫才能令聯合挑剔的人閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.23,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方是鋼彈合金製\N的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.10,0:13:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那是在衛星上製造的東西...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.71,0:13:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,15年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有我和你在這個OZ裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事就不會發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.88,0:13:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那果然是鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒其他可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.28,0:13:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合對宇宙的檢查太鬆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.52,0:13:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合的海軍想回收那機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.36,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那件事交由我們去辦就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會給你搜索海底的特殊部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後的拜託你知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.16,0:14:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明白吧，現在是重要時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.50,0:14:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想刺激聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.24,0:14:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.11,0:14:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯特校，我接到報告說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的部下衝入大氣層時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.78,0:14:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去了三部機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.19,0:14:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，那有甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是鎮壓叛亂分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就浪費了三部機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.29,0:14:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我們才能防範
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛亂分子的謀反於未然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.96,0:14:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說的不是結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.40,0:14:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你當聯合軍貴重的軍力是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.17,0:14:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貴重的軍力，那是指士兵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.14,0:14:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是指機動戰士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙在戲弄我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了，特列斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你今後要小心別犯同樣錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，有關今日的議題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.75,0:14:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻止殖民衛星聯手一事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.76,0:15:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合軍始終太習慣和平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後的時代由我們來創造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.36,0:15:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我的組織OZ創造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是個小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要動，救護車來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.78,0:15:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.84,0:15:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是...我是莉莉娜‧德利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.54,0:16:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事!?敵襲嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工場破壞任務完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.28,0:16:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後只差把所有敵人消滅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是杜巴基地!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現正受到敵人突襲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.36,0:16:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哪裡的攻襲!?不知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被發現了就不能放過你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的目的本來是破壞宇宙港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.27,0:16:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在要消滅一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥記錄001
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記錄者的名字是特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛亂分子的太空囊\N墜落在這附近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.56,0:17:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.49,0:17:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼也沒有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵襲!敵襲呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們被包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.01,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下武器投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會取你們性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊!攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.89,0:17:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是卡特爾，消滅了隊長機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.53,0:17:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫過你們投降啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.52,0:18:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是五飛，不會逃也不會躲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場戰爭馬上就會完結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海底搜索隊還沒來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.77,0:18:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說兩小時後到達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.57,0:18:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們慢吞吞做甚麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.54,0:18:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別那麼心急，那不會逃掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，這裡的海底很深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.58,0:18:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海軍要是搜索起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也應該須要很多時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.58,0:18:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外，讓你看些有趣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是OZ的偵察機拍到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我們交戰的那機種好相似吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，那機種有兩部!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.00,0:19:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，看來不只兩部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.13,0:19:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有報告說OZ的機動戰士工場、
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙港、以及像我們一樣前去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.84,0:19:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查落下太空囊的部隊也被毀滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說有4部?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加上沉在海裡那一部，總共5部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.52,0:19:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有5部鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們真幸運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.75,0:19:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我們目擊鋼彈後還能生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新學期才剛剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐就已經回校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.87,0:19:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真少見呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法啊，因為莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天才剛剛從宇宙回來
